'''Nerve disruptors''' were deadly weapons that, according to [[Jedi Master]] [[Lene Kostana]], were illegal in civilized [[star system]]s. When Kostana ventured to the [[planet]] [[Asusto]] with the [[Padawan]]s [[Dooku]] and [[Sifo-Dyas]], following the trail of supposed [[Dark side of the Force|dark side]] artifacts, they encountered a group of [[Abyssin]] [[smuggler]]s transporting nerve disruptors, intending to sell them. Enraged, Dooku [[Death|killed]] the Abyssin, destroying the nerve disruptors.<ref name="Dooku: Jedi Lost" />

